<ng-container [matColumnDef]="field">
  <mat-header-cell [class]="className" mat-header-cell *matHeaderCellDef>{{name}}</mat-header-cell>
  <mat-cell [class]="className" mat-cell *matCellDef="let element"
            (click)="element.model['field'] !== '' && openTooltip(reference,element)"
            #reference>
		<textarea matInput
              [(ngModel)]="element.model[field]"
              [disabled]="element.editable"
              [ngStyle]="{'color': 'black'}"></textarea>

    <ng-template #tooltipRef>
      <elix-tooltip [width]="width">{{vars}}</elix-tooltip>
    </ng-template>
  </mat-cell>
</ng-container>

styleUrlsData.data:
.package__item-content
  border: 1px solid
  overflow: auto

  .item-branch
    .package__item-content-child
      display: flex
      justify-content: space-between
      text-transform: capitalize
      height: 84vh

      .item-background__input
        background: var(--secondary-input-background)

      .package__item__content-per
        display: flex
        flex-direction: column
        justify-content: space-around

        .example-margin
          &:not(:checked)
            border: 1px solid var(--second-primary-text)
            border-radius: .3rem
            outline: none

components.templateData:
<div class="package__item-content" >
	<div class="item-branch" >
		<form #formDirective="ngForm" [formGroup]="items" >
			<div class="package__item-content-child p-5" >
				<div class="package__item__content-per" >
					<div class="flex-row" >
						<div ><span class="text-red-500" >*</span >
							Package Item ID
						</div >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input class="overflow-ellipsis item-background__input" elixTooltipDirective type="text" id="pckItemId"
							       readonly
							       style="border:none"
							       formControlName="pckItemId" >

						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span class="text-red-500" >*</span >
						<span >Item ID</span >
						<span >

            </span >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Hazmat Package Type ID</span >

							<input elixTooltipDirective id="hazmatPck" type="text" formControlName="hazmatPckTypeId" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Package weight</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="pckWeight" type="text" formControlName="pckWeight" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Package width</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="pckWidth" type="text" formControlName="pckWidth" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Unit Length</span >
						<div class="vorkurt__primary-input" >
							<input id="unitLength" type="text" formControlName="unitLength" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Diameter per Ship Unit</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="diameterPerShipUnit" type="text" formControlName="diameterPerShipUnit" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Package item Type ID</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="pckItemTypeId" type="text" formControlName="pckItemTypeId" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Inner Pack Packaging Unit</span >

						</div >

				</div >
				<div class="package__item__content-per" >
					<!--						middle-->
					<div >
						<span >Description</span >

							<textarea elixTooltipDirective id="description" formControlName="description" ></textarea >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Priority</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="priority" type="text" formControlName="priority" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Packaging unit</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="pckUnit" type="text" formControlName="pckUnit" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Unit Volume</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="unitVolume" type="text" formControlName="unitVolume" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Unit width</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="unitWidth" type="text" formControlName="unitWidth" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Core Diameter</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="coreDiameter" type="text" formControlName="coreDiameter" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >THU Profile ID</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="thuProfileId" type="text" formControlName="thuProfileId" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Inner Pack Size</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="innerPackSize" type="text" formControlName="innerPackSize" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Compartment Type Profile ID</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="compartmentTypeProfileId" type="text" formControlName="compartmentTypeProfileId" >
						</div >
					</div >
				</div >
				<div class="package__item__content-per" >
					<div >
						<span >Hazaradous</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<mat-checkbox
                  formControlName="hazaradous"
                class="example-margin"
							              [checked]="false"
							              [color]="'primary'" >

							</mat-checkbox >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div class="mt-20" >
						<span >Mixable</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<mat-checkbox
                formControlName="mixable"
                class="example-margin"
							              [checked]="false"
							              [color]="'primary'" >

							</mat-checkbox >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Default Packaging</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<mat-checkbox
                formControlName="defaultPck"
                class="example-margin"
							              [checked]="false"
							              [color]="'primary'" >

							</mat-checkbox >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Unit Height</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="unitHeight" type="text" formControlName="unitHeight" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Load Config Rule Rank</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="loadConfigRuleRank" type="text" formControlName="loadConfigRuleRank" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Inner Pack Size UOM Code </span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input id="innerPckSizeUOMcode" type="text" formControlName="innerPckSizeUOMcode" >
						</div >
					</div >
					<div >
						<span >Category ID</span >
						<div elixInputPrimary >
							<input elixTooltipDirective class="overflow-ellipsis item-background__input" id="categoryId" type="text"
							       formControlName="categoryId" >
						</div >
					</div >
				</div >
			</div >
		</form >
	</div >
</div >

components.name: PageComponent
components.template:
Pages in Storybook

We recommend building UIs with a component-driven process starting with atomic components and ending with pages.

Render pages with mock data. This makes it easy to build and review page states without needing to navigate to them in your app. Here are some handy patterns for managing page data in Storybook:

  • Use a higher-level connected component. Storybook helps you compose such data from the "args" of child component stories
  • Assemble data in the page component from your services. You can mock these services out using Storybook.

Get a guided tutorial on component-driven development at Storybook tutorials . Read more in the docs .

Tip Adjust the width of the canvas with the Viewports addon in the toolbar
